@startuml 1A_Tenant_Registration
title 1-A · Tenant Registration & Activation (UC-L05 to UC-L09)

start
|Visitor (Prospective Tenant)|
:Open pricing page and select a subscription plan;
:Fill tenant registration form\n(tenant name, slug, admin email, password);
if (Selected plan is paid?) then (Yes)
  :Provide payment details;
else (No)
  :Continue with free plan;
endif

|System|
:Validate tenant name, slug, email,\npassword and selected plan;
if (Validation passed?) then (No)
  :Return 422 validation error\n(email/slug/plan/password);
  stop
else (Yes)
  if (Payment required?) then (Yes)
    :Process payment through selected PaymentStrategy;
    if (Payment successful?) then (No)
      :Create Tenant with status = PENDING;
      :Prompt visitor to retry payment;
      stop
    else (Yes)
      :Continue tenant provisioning;
    endif
  else (No)
    :Skip payment step;
  endif
endif

|System|
:Create Tenant record\nstatus = ACTIVE;
:Create TenantConfig with default settings;
:Create TenantAdmin / User account;
:Create TenantSubscription for selected plan;
:Send verification email to admin email;
:Return bearer token and redirect to Tenant Admin;

|Tenant Admin (Owner)|
:Verify email address;
:Complete initial tenant setup\n(branding, idol profile, domain if needed);

|System|
:Save setup data and mark onboarding complete;
:Tenant Admin can operate the idol fansite;
stop
@enduml
